Hip-hop artist M.I Abaga has released his first official single of the year entitled “Daddy”. MI said the new song aims to celebrate women while appraising their beauty. “Daddy is a song that’s here to celebrate our women and further appraise their beauty,” he said.   Mercy Aigbe mourns Kaduna train attack victims, urges…     Ubi Franklin dares Timaya to carry out beating threat     Actress Laide Bakare flaunts new mansion   “Daddy” is the lead single off M.I’s forthcoming project that promises to be more than exciting for his fans. In the new song, M.I Abaga features Chillz to create what has been dubbed an exciting masterpiece by critics after the song’s release. MI Abaga is a household name, who has won several awards and released critically acclaimed commercially successful albums.